* Restructuring and strengthening WEC:
* The existing WECS will be turned into WEC.  Thereafter, WEC will be
* Restructure the existing WEC members into a consultative and advisory
* Provide mandatory authority to WEC through the Transaction of Government
* WEC to provide techno-economic clearance to water resources projects.
	* Hydropower projects of more than 10 MW installed capacity;
	* Irrigation projects of more than 5,000 ha command area;
	* Drinking water supply projects covering more than 100,000 population;
	* River training projects covering a river stretch of more than 10 km,
	* Projects designed for multipurpose use;
